<div class='documentTop'><div>
  
  
    <h1>Accreditation of election observers</h1>
  
  </div></div>
  

  <div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">   
  <div>
    <p>National and international organisations and institutions wishing to observe elections in Norway must apply to the Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development for accreditation. For further information about the requirements for an application for accreditation, please see the <a href="/en/dep/krd/kampanjer/election_portal/election-observation/guidelines-for-election-observers.html?id=573465">Ministry’s Guidelines for election observers</a>.</p>
<p>Accredited election observers are formally authorised and empowered to observe the whole election process. Proof of accreditation applies for the individual election for which accreditation is applied, and is issued to individuals. </p>
<p>The Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development will issue proof of accreditation to all election observers who fulfil the requirements. </p>
<p>The electoral authorities at both central and local government level shall ensure that the observers have unrestricted access to all stages of the electoral process. Election observers shall be able to move freely around the country and meet with the organisations and persons of their choice. Election observers shall decide themselves what they wish to observe, and where. </p>
<h3>Accreditation card</h3>
<p>This is a card that election observers shall always wear in a visible position while observing an election. </p>
<p>Example of card:</p>
<p><img alt="Illustration of an accreditation card" src="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/akkrediteringskort_engelsk.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<h3>&nbsp;</h3>
<h3>Register of accredited observers</h3>
<p>The Ministry maintains an overview of all accredited observers. The register is updated continuously.</p>
<p>142 election observers are accredited&nbsp;to observe the Parliamentary Election and Sami Assembly Election 2009.</p>
<p>See an <a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Liste_valgobservatorer09_engelsk.pdf">overview of all accredited observers</a> (pdf-format)<br /></p>
  </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
